r-of-new-species-in-the-ocean-depths</link><description>其中&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-discovered-a-record-number-of-new-species-in-the-ocean-depths.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 01:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-discovered-a-record-number-of-new-species-in-the-ocean-depths</guid></item><item><title>为了研究芯片的真正工作原理，麻省理工学院的研究人员构建了自己的操作系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/to-study-how-chips-really-work-mit-researchers-built-their-own-operating-system</link><description>当安全研究人员想要了解现代处理器到底在做什么，以及决定是否可能发生 Spectre 和 Meltdown 等攻击的细节时，他们通常在从未为此工作构建的操作系统上运行实验。他们打开 macOS 或 Linux，手动修补内核，并希望修改能够保留。该方法不稳定，难以重现，并且在 Apple 平台上将被弃用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/to-study-how-chips-really-work-mit-researchers-built-their-own-operating-system.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 01:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/to-study-how-chips-really-work-mit-researchers-built-their-own-operating-system</guid></item><item><title>世界上第一个人造鸡蛋孵化出小鸡</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/chickens-hatch-from-worlds-first-artificial-eggs</link><description>5 月 19 日，总部位于达拉斯的 Colossal Biosciences 公司宣布，它已经用完全人造的鸡蛋孵化出了 26 只活的小鸡。去年，该公司成功地消灭了恐狼，成为头条新闻。这一突破背后的技术稍后可用于拯救渡渡鸟和新西兰巨大的、不会飞的恐鸟——它们都在 Colossal 的反灭绝“待办事项”清单上……&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/chickens-hatch-from-worlds-first-artificial-eggs.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 00:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/chickens-hatch-from-worlds-first-artificial-eggs</guid></item><item><title>中国将人工智能大脑植入物从试验转向实际使用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/china-moves-ai-brain-implants-from-trials-towards-real-world-use</link><description>中国的初创公司正在加紧努力开发脑机接口算法，帮助人们行走和说话。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/china-moves-ai-brain-implants-from-trials-towards-real-world-use.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 00:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/china-moves-ai-brain-implants-from-trials-towards-real-world-use</guid></item><item><title>认知科学家说你不存在 |约沙·巴赫</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-cognitive-scientist-who-says-you-dont-exist-joscha-bach</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 00:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-cognitive-scientist-who-says-you-dont-exist-joscha-bach</guid></item><item><title>唯物主义阻碍了科学吗？ |亚当·弗兰克、丽莎·费尔德曼·巴雷特、迈克尔·莱文</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/is-materialism-holding-science-back-adam-frank-lisa-feldman-barrett-michael-levin</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 00:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/is-materialism-holding-science-back-adam-frank-lisa-feldman-barrett-michael-levin</guid></item><item><title>也许新的量子处理技术预示着晶体管之后的生活</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-quantum-processing-technology-points-to-life-after-the-transistor-maybe</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 23:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-quantum-processing-technology-points-to-life-after-the-transistor-maybe</guid></item></channel></rss>